    "1663667029efc274af": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "cd3d35fb-4237-4e0c-b360-523aae405e51": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What are the specific dimensions of the ultralight double hammock?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>The unpacked dimensions of the anymaka ultralight double hammock are 141*86 in / 358*220 cm. When folded into its stuff sack, the packed dimensions are 4.3*4.3*6.7 in / 11*11*17 cm.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "5586f39f-c9cc-41a5-9c79-494141a820e1": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What material does it use?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>The anymaka ultralight double hammock is crafted from 40D diamond ripstop nylon fabric, which is super durable and lightweight enough to carry around.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "78977bda-88c1-4c5d-a57b-395a8e01f169": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is the wiregate carabiners durable enough?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>The wiregate carabiners are made of climbing-grade aluminum, ensuring secure and reliable hanging for your hammock.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "6ca4af54-3f47-4d4d-9060-0ff238ab6d1a": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How should I care for my hammock?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Keep your hammock away from direct sunlight when you're not using it, and store it in a cool, dry place. When washing, take off carabiners first, use cold water and mild detergent, then let it air dry. <strong>We only recommend hand washing. </strong>If you need further cleaning, machine wash with the following instructions:</p><ul><li>Wash hammock in cold water</li><li>Do not dry clean</li><li>Do not tumble dry</li><li>Do not iron</li></ul>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
